1. *Uradimo* još jednu stvar prije odlaska (Let's do one more thing before leaving).
2. Popravićemo sve u jednom danu, *uradićemo* to zajedno (We will fix everything in one day, we will do it together).
3. Moraćemo da *uradimo* još mnogo rada (We will have to do a lot more work).
4. Želim da *uradim* ovo sam (I want to do this myself).
5. Da li ćemo *uraditi* to za dogovoreno vreme? (Will we do it by the agreed time?).